<li id="mwKA"><b id="mwKQ">L2.</b> <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/결합법칙" title="결합법칙" id="mwKg">결합법칙</a>: <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt3" data-mw="{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;math&quot;,&quot;attrs&quot;:{},&quot;body&quot;:{&quot;extsrc&quot;:&quot;(A \\otimes B) \\otimes C = A \\otimes (B \\otimes C)&quot;}}" id="mwKw"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle (A\otimes B)\otimes C=A\otimes (B\otimes C)}">
